<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the protrusion of the rod.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="F043108E08" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Protrusion of the rod</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>1.5 to 2.5 mm (0.059 to 0.098 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the protrusion is not within the specified range, adjust it.</ptxt>
<atten2>
<ptxt>Do not depress the brake pedal.</ptxt>
</atten2>
</s2>
